{"tid":1918081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港之光] 曹星如成日同黑警教官跑步wo","createTime":"2020-03-10T01:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T02:32:57.000Z","uid":132380,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4df940be1a4140eee0c6f488216a4e67527c97bc","tid":1918081,"uid":132380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:02:09.000Z","msg":"呢幾日，全港體育記者係度吹捧曹星如，話佢係香港之光，香港精神。咁唔知同黑警跑步，仲要放上網威威既曹星如，點睇都係深藍啦？佢仲要唔係同普通警察，仲要用香港警察既面書有推介過既黃竹坑警校教官，即係教到而家d黑警出黎又打又抽水又講粗口既教官，仲有聽講係香港01既記者一齊係警暴橫行，日日黑警死全家果陣，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曹星如，香港01記者同黑警教官一齊開開心心跑步仲要放上網，咁係咪攻入中大果日改下黑頭像，就做返黃呢？ 點呀，你地「定性」左未呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6y72i3y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6y72i3y.jpg&h=a22db9f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DmuoNWW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDmuoNWW.jpg&h=f212037b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4fbc683566e351814c1e49de81c27b8ca845f5b","tid":1918081,"uid":132380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:04:58.000Z","msg":"星如加油"},{"pid":"851e4526e633b5bd15beb7f3612ceda1279e829f","tid":1918081,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:05:33.000Z","msg":"如如加油"},{"pid":"4eaec1b540362c41e68eb8e72432f234469bde4f","tid":1918081,"uid":132380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"851e4526e633b5bd15beb7f3612ceda1279e829f","tid":1918081,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:05:33.000Z","msg":"如如加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:06:15.000Z","msg":"如如係HK star, 不割"},{"pid":"41683bc6651c5dd665296f8590cabded730011ce","tid":1918081,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:07:17.000Z","msg":"我地一齊like香港黑警個page 早日突破40萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1918074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1918074</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1588de4ebe667d988ec5d0d24229257d12659c","tid":1918081,"uid":132380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:38:17.000Z","msg":"I love yuyu"},{"pid":"3d96c876a707585ae9466a01b5a8c2497d67653f","tid":1918081,"uid":25367,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"香港運動員九成都藍<br />\n君如肯定有份教黑警打人"},{"pid":"12d3003546bf9ab29e591812bfe35f464918ff87","tid":1918081,"uid":107681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3d96c876a707585ae9466a01b5a8c2497d67653f","tid":1918081,"uid":25367,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"香港運動員九成都藍<br />\n君如肯定有份教黑警打人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:43:22.000Z","msg":"會輸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6235312b68bd5b641a2ac2f6963f5fc8b3531ab0","tid":1918081,"uid":191926,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"好多運動員同黑警有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警本身相當多人<br />\n就有玩不同運動<br />\n<br />\n6，7月仲有同黑警聯繫 唔係奇事<br />\n連登6月前 都有黑警討論post, 招募post <br />\n佔中後黑警用左4年時間洗底<br />\n<br />\n但到左9月，10月 <br />\n仲同黑警friend 到 出post<br />\n<br />\n只可以講 4個字黃極有限"},{"pid":"3ebe908df80932804f4ee7cc2c32f0f0e7ec5baa","tid":1918081,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呀澤同王喜都撐如如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>仲要如如有上過呀澤個節目《杜汶澤食住上》ep08<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VdP8eSD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdP8eSD.jpg&h=3b290afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「神奇小子」曹星如（Rex）昨晚於灣仔會展，力戰日本前世界冠軍河野公平，Rex最終以點數獲勝，成功衛冕WBO超蠅量級國際拳王金腰帶，職業生涯已取得22連勝，不過Rex因激戰撼傷前額，令左眼腫如雞蛋，要急送院治理，今午Rex透過instagram向粉絲平安。<br />\n<br />\nRex向來都有不少圈中fans，昨晚捧場藝人包括徐濠縈﹑鄭希怡﹑王喜和陳志雲等，而靚媽林嘉欣亦有觀戰，並留言激讚：「好感動啊！人生第一次看拳擊比賽就這麼精彩！曹星如，你好棒好打得！Proud of You!」在現場睇賽事的杜汶澤，見證Rex的22連勝後，亦在facebook貼圖留言恭喜對方：「Rex Win﹗」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20171008/1507443873307/【曹星如22連勝】杜汶澤貼圖恭喜-林嘉欣激讚-好感動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20171008%2F1507443873307%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9B%B9%E6%98%9F%E5%A6%8222%E9%80%A3%E5%8B%9D%E3%80%91%E6%9D%9C%E6%B1%B6%E6%BE%A4%E8%B2%BC%E5%9C%96%E6%81%AD%E5%96%9C-%E6%9E%97%E5%98%89%E6%AC%A3%E6%BF%80%E8%AE%9A-%E5%A5%BD%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=21a025df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20171008%2F1507443873307%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9B%B9%E6%98%9F%E5%A6%8222%E9%80%A3%E5%8B%9D%E3%80%91%E6%9D%9C%E6%B1%B6%E6%BE%A4%E8%B2%BC%E5%9C%96%E6%81%AD%E5%96%9C-%E6%9E%97%E5%98%89%E6%AC%A3%E6%BF%80%E8%AE%9A-%E5%A5%BD%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95&h=4c6b3321\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20171008/1507443873307/【曹星如22連勝】杜汶澤貼圖恭喜-林嘉欣激讚-好感動</a>"},{"pid":"f8469cffba356729a3fe59b1b6bddd62e929a9db","tid":1918081,"uid":188176,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:57:37.000Z","msg":"呢條所謂拳王不嬲廢<br />\n未撚打過勁人<br />\n夾埋自己人屈鳩個三十幾歲既前拳王輸點數<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e82adfa6c4046c40f659a248d189c13f055675","tid":1918081,"uid":132380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ebe908df80932804f4ee7cc2c32f0f0e7ec5baa","tid":1918081,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:55:3